CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 27, 1969, reads: "DANDY DUFFERS PARTY - Gathered at the Club Loendi, in a recent social hour, were these members of the Dandy Duffers Golf and Country Club. Seated from left: Louise Hinton, Aurelia Johnson, Georgianna Miles, Kathleen Halloway [Holloway]. Standing (first row): Tournament Chairman Charles Hinton, Jack Hopkins, Jack Kelley, Wesley Carr, Henry Lee, Harry Irvin, Champion Dave Doggins and Vice-President Sterling Perkins. Back row - Clarence Bruce, Joe Preston, John White, Luther Thomas, John Henderson, Charles Berry, Garland Morton." - Harris Photo
TitMainTitle: Members of Dandy Duffers Golf club holding trophies and gathered in Loendi Club, including from left: Louise Hinton, Aurelia Johnson, Georgianna Miles, Kathleen Holloway; second row: Tournament Chairman Charles Hinton, Jack Hopkins, Jack Kelley, Wesley Carr, Henry Lee, Harry Irvin, Champion Dave Doggins and Vice-President Sterling Perkins; back row: Clarence Bruce, Joe Preston, John White, Luther Thomas, John Henderson, Charles Berry, Garland Morton
